{"tid":1279274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］如何捍衛連登？","createTime":"2019-07-02T15:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T22:05:21.000Z","uid":12661,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e88837cb1daeaaf967e5738402f7985077f3d789","tid":1279274,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"我諗頭先上唔到連登嘅巴打絲打一定覺得好恐怖&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果大陸網軍去攻擊 Cloudflare，我唔太擔心，諒佢哋都無辦法打低美國佬&hellip; 但係如果佢哋選擇性淨係攻擊連登呢？今日嘅連登頂唔頂得住呢？<br />\n<br />\n有唔少討論，建議我哋一齊搬去一啲外國嘅討論區，我唔係 IT 人，唔知外國討論區嘅配備，係咪就足夠抵擋大陸網軍？<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果我哋咁做，對唔對得住撐咗個壇、撐咗我哋咁耐嘅連尼住、望遠巴打？佢哋投入咗咁多嘅心血同精力，係咪就咁毀於一旦、血本無歸？<br />\n<br />\n如果倚賴外國技術就可以保護呢個論壇，我哋可唔可以用行動支持連仔，幫連登嘅裝置升級？如果有需要，我唔介意參加眾籌，亦特此呼籲，希望大家喺呢度享受咗咁多自由討論空間嘅巴打絲打，都可以繼續支持連登！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71776357db8ecd6303e818285b3d7a35b835c53b","tid":1279274,"uid":98839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"818aaa7f22fd32a7529d980cf7997dd9fa6311cf","tid":1279274,"uid":180807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5c03c9bb3601076c3a851241964615bf6b8efd7","tid":1279274,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"上唔到連登 就去登記做選民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後半個鐘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>今晚2359截</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c2c181fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io</a><br />\n直接網上填表唔洗寄3分鐘搞掂<br />\n[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f4356679\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=28bb2cbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=06b16a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用email/fax交 今晚1200截</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=8b69cb24\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"c2b12d6ce62e1686bd522ccea325729dabc31a1c","tid":1279274,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"推下先！"},{"pid":"ac0bdf2e9d3edcaabd60fe26d764c5014621d955","tid":1279274,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"如果用咗cloudflare都可以繞過cloudflare直打個host咁邊有人會用cloudflare"},{"pid":"9020f25d338fc293181d6f68071ca34f246f38da","tid":1279274,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"Cloudflare就係連登個盾攻擊連登＝ 攻擊Cloudflare"},{"pid":"381959e562ec44e1ac104ea8713121a9a6dfa46a","tid":1279274,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac0bdf2e9d3edcaabd60fe26d764c5014621d955","tid":1279274,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:48:53.000Z","msg":"如果用咗cloudflare都可以繞過cloudflare直打個host咁邊有人會用cloudflare"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"利申：唔識 IT <br />\n<br />\n如果對手用其他方法攻擊呢？ cloudflare 係咪都可以抵擋？"},{"pid":"12735058fc8c0cf4b75f5c0a07994c04573c2796","tid":1279274,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a32bcd92f58f1855cbed1121921edb1341aaafb","tid":1279274,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76a9311f71844d7e710c76935d2ffd3315bce529","tid":1279274,"uid":1266